[SN]TITLE[SN]
Biker 'wheelied past police car' in Aberdeen

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A motorcyclist and pillion passenger were filmed doing a wheelie as they passed a police car in Aberdeen.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The incident happened in the city's South College Street on Thursday.
Police Scotland said officers were investigating.
A spokesperson, appealing for witnesses, added: "It would have created further risk to the public to pursue the vehicle. Further enquiries have been carried out including reviewing CCTV footage."
